title: Ep 37 - How to Grow Your Bank Account
itunes:title: Ep 37 - How to Grow Your Bank Account
description:
Everyone wants a bigger bank account but most people don't know that one of the fastest ways to grow their bank accounts is to focus on growing themselves first. In this episode Rob talks about how your bank account only grows when you personal development account has grown.
